{"questionId":"9084979","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The beam is produced by accelerating electrons through an electric potential difference <em>U</em>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>A typical interatomic distance in the graphite crystal is of the order of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></math> m. Estimate the minimum value of <em>U</em> for the pattern in (a) to be formed on the screen.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>The de Broglie wavelength of the electrons should be comparable to or shorter than the interatomic distance /&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></math> m&nbsp;✓</p>\n<p>Momentum of electrons&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>≈</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>63</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>34</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp;«<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math> N s» ✓</p>\n<p>Kinetic energy of electrons = «<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>11</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>31</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo></math>»<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>18</mn></mrow></msup></math> «J»&nbsp;&nbsp;✓</p>\n<p>